OL,3,CWoman, 95, left lying on pavement for
OL,4,Cover five hours before ambulance
OL,5,Carrived
OL,7,FA 95-year-old lady from Dorset, who
OL,8,Ffell and broke her hip, was left lying
OL,9,Fon a cold pavement for over five hours
OL,10,Fbefore an ambulance arrived.
OL,12,FWinifred Soanes said to her husband of
OL,13,Fover 60 years that she thought she was
OL,14,Fgoing to die.
OL,16,FPassers-by on Christchurch High Street
OL,17,Fprovided blankets and hot water
OL,18,Fbottles for the pensioner.
OL,20,FWinifred is still in hospital
OL,21,Frecovering after her hip operation.
