OL,5,Carrived
OL,7,FHer husband Arthur Soanes said: "She
OL,8,Fthought she was going to die, after
OL,9,Ftwo or three hours because she was
OL,10,Fgetting cold from the pavement.
OL,12,F"She really thought she was going to
OL,13,Fdie but bless her she thought of me as
OL,14,Fwell at that time and she was worrying
OL,15,Fhow I was gonna manage but that's Win."
OL,17,FWhen describing his marriage he said:
OL,18,F"61 glorious years and I hope we have
OL,19,Fa few more left.
