OL,3,CWoman, 95, left lying on pavement for
OL,4,Cover five hours before ambulance
OL,5,Carrived
OL,7,F"I miss her for everything because
OL,8,Fshe's my eyes really."
OL,10,FArthur is visually impaired and he
OL,11,F'relies totally on his 95-year-old
OL,12,Fwife.'
OL,14,FHe said the hours waiting on
OL,15,FChristchurch High Street were
OL,16,Ftraumatic, for them both.
OL,18,FHe said: "She's my life and I couldn't
OL,19,Fbelieve how long we had to wait and
OL,20,Fwait, each minute was like an hour it
OL,21,Fwas terrible
