OL,5,Carrived
OL,7,FJane Chandler, Executive Director of
OL,8,FQuality Patient Care at the South
OL,9,FWestern Ambulance Service NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust, said: "We would like
OL,11,Fto offer our sincere apologies to Mrs
OL,12,FSoanes for the delay in our response.
OL,14,F"The delay was unacceptable and falls
OL,15,Fbelow the high standards of care we
OL,16,Faim to provide.
OL,18,F"Delays in our care is not something
OL,19,Fwe want any of our patients to
OL,20,Fexperience, and when a delay does
OL,21,Foccur, it's taken very seriously.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
