OL,7,F"Our response to Mrs Soanes will be
OL,8,Freviewed and any learnings will be
OL,9,Fimplemented, to help improve our
OL,10,Fservice to patients.
OL,12,F"At the time of Mrs Soanes' fall, our
OL,13,Fservice was under extreme pressure,
OL,14,Fand our response time was impacted by
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,17,F"This demand was further compounded by
OL,18,Fhospital handover delays and system
OL,19,Fpressures within the wider NHS and
OL,20,Fsocial care.
